title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 75: Featuring Feitelberg, Chief, Nick Maraldo and Jordie
description:
On this episode, we have a handful of Barstool's #HockeyGuys check in to discuss the first two nights of the NHL playoffs. Chief (Chicago) gives us his take on the goings-on out West. Nick Maraldo (Heartland) fills us in on his Penguins and other East series. Feitelberg (Boston) checks in to praise his Bruins and slam Nazem Kadri. And Jordie (Philly) does his standard lamenting about his Flyers and their coach.Â 


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
